column3:
The Battle Tower is exactly what it sounds like.
{pageend:It’s a place where you can have Pokémon battles.}
You can try Single Battles and Double Battles,
{pageend:and then their Master Classes.}
{pageend:If you win, you can earn Rare Candies and BP.}
Feel free to battle to hone your skill as a Trainer.

Greetings, Pokémon Trainer.
{pageend:I bare an invitation.}
You have been invited to a battle by
{pageend:the world's greatest Pokémon.}
Please accept this invitation and
attend me at the Gate.

Hm? Where am I..?
{pageend:This is the Battleground?}
I don’t understand what happened...
{pageend:But your Pokémon need healing, right?}
A true Pokémon nurse never rests!
Speak to me if your team needs help.
